Text: I'm sure it's a very large book, but what's it about exactly? At least some clue to what it is, and you'll probably get a lot more downloaders. One such as myself perhaps, if it's interesting.
Death-Dude, if you don't know that it is you either don't need it or aren't ready. Thanks heaps pgnds - sux heaps that you can't buy this anywhere for Kindle.
